name: Noemia Reis Capoeira

locations.name: University of Alaska Anchorage
locations.rawText: Capoeira at University of Alaska Anchorage taught by Noemia Reis. It is a university class, so you have to sign up at the beginning of each semester. There is only one class, so there is a mixture of beginners and more experienced students in it. It is a three hour, once weekly class.

notes: Currently gives dance classes that include some aspects of capoeira, but the classes aren't advertised as such. She has thought about giving classes that focus solely on capoeira. People here in Anchorage have expressed interest in learning capoeira. Email 9/3/02: thinking about starting a capoeira class here soon. Email 9/9/02
